'''相场模型'''是一种求解界面问题的数学模型，主要用于求解凝固动力学，<ref>[http://arjournals.annualreviews.org/doi/abs/10.1146/annurev.matsci.32.101901.155803  WJ. Boettinger et al. Annual Review of Materials Research Vol. 32: 163-194 (2002)]</ref>但也可以应用于其他问题，比如[[粘性指进|粘性指进]]、<ref name=viscous>[http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRE/v60/i2/p1734_1 R. Folch et al. Phys. Rev. E 60, 1734 - 1740 (1999)]</ref> [[断裂动力学|断裂动力学]]、<ref>[http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v87/i4/e045501 A. Karma et al. Phys. Rev. Lett. 87, 045501 (2001)]</ref> [[囊泡|囊泡]]动力学<ref>[http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevE.72.041921 T. Biben et al. Phys. Rev. E 72, 041921 (2005)]</ref>、[[高分子|高分子]][[单晶|单晶]]<ref name="anlijia">{{cite journal | title=Simulated morphological landscape of polymer single crystals by phase field model | author=Dong Wang, Tongfei Shi, Jizhong Chen, Lijia An, Yuxi Jia | journal=THE JOURNAL OF CHEMICAL PHYSICS | volume=129 | issue=19 | pages=194903|date=November 2008}}</ref>等等。

相场模型回避了界面处的边界条件，代之以辅助场（相场）的演化。相场为体系的[[序参量|序参量]]。相场在两相取不同的值，在界面附近区域连续地从一相的值变为另一相的值。

相场模型是菲克斯<ref>G.J. Fix, in Free Boundary Problems: Theory and Applications, Ed. A. Fasano and M. Primicerio, p. 580, Pitman (Boston, 1983).</ref> 和兰格,<ref>J.S. Langer, Models of pattern formation in ﬁrst–order phase transitions, in Directions in Condensed Matter Physics p. 165, Ed. G. Grinstein and G. Mazenko, World Scientiﬁc, Singapore, (1986).</ref> 首先引入的，在凝固和各种问题中有着越来越广泛的应用。

